AUDIO: 'is of course really cool because now we have it&nbsp; kind of private, you know, and only for our use,&nbsp;&nbsp; which is of course really cool. So only thing&nbsp; which is important is that you leave the window&nbsp;&nbsp; open. By the way, the installation can take&nbsp; up to 10 to 15 minutes. So, make sure to&nbsp;&nbsp;'

